Author: OodietcokeheadoO
Text: In my experience it never really changes much telling people. I've never really hidden it but I underplay it a lot and have everyone convinced I know what I'm doing and I'm fine. It's never come up more than once with anyone.

Author: athrowawayCNA16
Text: I don't know how to help you because I'd just give you terrible advise, but you're getting all of my love and support! It's so scary opening up that can of worms, but know your friends love you and want to support you.
